Bank.=C2=A0
One concession was a roughly $430 million loan from SoftBank to Neumann tha=
t had a key feature: Neumann wasn=E2=80=99t personally on the hook for payi=
ng it back. Instead, if he stopped paying, SoftBank would be able to seize =
his shares in WeWork as collateral.
The value of that collateral has plummeted. With WeWork=E2=80=99s stock pri=
ce near zero, Neumann=E2=80=99s WeWork shares are currently worth $4 millio=
