The data here is slim: ProPublica has some tax forms, which report Buffett=
=E2=80=99s=C2=A0sales=C2=A0but not his purchases, so there are no findings =
like =E2=80=9Che bought a stock a week before Berkshire Hathaway did.=E2=80=
=9D Sometimes he=C2=A0sold=C2=A0stock around the same time that Berkshire d=
id. Other times, he sold stock around the same time that Berkshire was buyi=
